Preheat the oven to 240°C/220°C fan/gas mark 9.

Chop the @baby potatoes{500%g} into 2cm chunks.

Pop onto a large (lined) #baking tray{}. Toss with @salt{1/4%tsp}, @pepper{to taste} and a drizzle of @oil{to taste}. Spread out in a single layer.

When the oven is hot, roast on the top shelf until golden, ~{25-35%minutes}. Turn the tray halfway through.

When the potatoes have 5 mins left to cook, sprinkle half the @sesame seeds{1%sachet} over the top. Return to the oven for the remaining time.

Meanwhile, peel and grate the @garlic{2}(peeled and grated) (or use a #garlic press{}).

Trim and quarter the @radish{125%g}(trimmed and quartered).

Trim the @salad leaves{120%g}(trimmed), then tear into bite-sized pieces or thinly slice widthways.

Just before serving, toss the salad leaves and radish together with the @sweet Asian sauce{1%sachet}. Season to taste with @salt{to taste} and @pepper{to taste}.

== Turkey Burgers ==

In a #large bowl{}, combine the @turkey mince{250%g}, @breadcrumbs{1%pack}, remaining @sesame seeds{1%sachet}, garlic, @water{1%tbsp} and @salt{1/4%tsp} (double both for 4p).

Season with pepper and mix together by hand.

Roll into evenly-sized balls, then shape into 1cm thick burgers, one per person.

> IMPORTANT: Wash hands and equipment after handling raw mince.

Place a #large pan{} over medium-high heat with a drizzle of @oil{to taste}.

Once hot, fry the burgers until browned on the outside and cooked through, ~{10-12%minutes}.

Carefully turn the burgers every ~{3-4%minutes}, adjusting the heat if needed.

Cover and cook for the final ~{3-4%minutes}.

> IMPORTANT: Burgers are cooked when no longer pink in the middle.

== Spicy Miso Honey Drizzle ==

While your burgers cook, make your drizzle by adding the @mayo{1%sachet}, @miso paste{1%sachet}, @gochujang paste{2%sachets} and @honey{1%sachet} to a #bowl{}.

Mix well to combine.

> TIP: If your honey has hardened, pop the sachet into a bowl of warm water for 1-2 mins.

== Serving ==

Divide the sesame potatoes between plates.

Serve the turkey burger and salad alongside.

Top the burger with the spicy miso honey drizzle.